      <title>Reddit 强劲的交易开局在股价大周面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/reddit-s-strong-trading-start-faces-test-in-big-week-for-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc. 股价上涨 67%，成为今年最热门的新上市公司之一，但季度业绩和内部人士卖出限制的到期即将考验这一涨幅。]]></description>
