    <item>
      <title>加密货币 ETF 综合体在首次重大压力测试中遭遇抛售狂潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/crypto-etf-complex-hit-by-selling-spree-in-first-big-stress-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球市场崩溃，加密货币这一投机资产类别自今年早些时候通过 ETF 进入主流以来首次遭遇大规模抛售，投资者从加密货币相关基金中撤出了近 5 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/crypto-etf-complex-hit-by-selling-spree-in-first-big-stress-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:46:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Groq 28 亿美元估值缓解了人们对人工智能的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/groq-s-2-8-billion-valuation-tamps-down-ai-fears-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能初创公司 Groq 筹集了 6.4 亿美元的新资金，凸显了投资者对人工智能系统芯片创新的热情。Groq 首席执行官乔纳森·罗斯 (Jonathan Ross) 与艾德·拉德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 一起参加“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/groq-s-2-8-billion-valuation-tamps-down-ai-fears-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
